
Hermit is a boot loader/downloader combination for embedded software
development.  It is designed to support multiple targets with a common
infrastructure, although at present only one target (the Cirrus Logic
EDB7211 evaluation board) is supported.

The latest version of hermit can be found at:
http://web.bluemug.com/~miket/arm/

Build and installation instructions can be found in the INSTALL file.

